{"tid":1444464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手段一定要進化，突破現況討論","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:50:22.000Z","uid":147317,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8f3ac7e56e0eebbc4f7a0cdc93d47ba418c146bb","tid":1444464,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:31:39.000Z","msg":"尋日我寫左一個post，不過無乜人理我<br />\n<br />\n我地係輸緊，但香港人係能夠突破困局<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441965</a><br />\n<br />\n我想講我地依家已經輸緊，班賤人已經打經濟，想拉散我地既支持，長此落去我哋好快會俾人反cap <br />\n<br />\n我認為而家最緊要嘅大方向係宣傳要突破同溫層，我哋唔能夠只係喺網上面宣傳，依家每個星期嘅光復運動每次都係同狗對抗 ，我哋應該轉為同當地居民宣傳，要講清楚我地既目標，狗同政府既賤格野。要突破現況，我地既手段都要突破！<br />\n<br />\n好多人會問，我地點解要民意？因為我地要足夠支持做大型反擊<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得點解我地會成功 ？ deadline 升級呢樣嘢我地要用多次<br />\n<br />\n係宣傳既時候，我地要俾賤婦777 9月中前要回應，如果唔係我地9月尾就<br />\n<br />\n1.四罷 - 罷工罷課罷市罷買<br />\n2.大型示威<br />\n3.不合作運動<br />\n4.衝擊所有十一活動<br />\n5.追擊所有官員<br />\n<br />\n我地要大型反攻，唔能夠俾土共贏架"},{"pid":"08f0c907599e9d19d59bd6c73e79aa63e7dda1eb","tid":1444464,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"推十次"},{"pid":"2b9d6fa6241698224dae60de98e1f17bd05e061f","tid":1444464,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bf27dfdc1d0ee53bb94504d2244cd3018f3f7a","tid":1444464,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235a8fcddf0960f000c07306e25f9467e9b1d489","tid":1444464,"uid":147317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor